Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.92,0:00:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亞少年 魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.08,0:00:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有兩種力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其一是Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠對任何人下達命令並讓其絕對遵守的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.34,0:00:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其二是黑之騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.60,0:00:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了毀滅他父皇統治的布里塔尼亞帝國而存在的 屬於他自己的軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修以ZERO這個代號開始行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了替母后報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.23,0:00:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是為了創造妹妹娜娜莉能夠幸福生活的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.51,0:00:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其行動究竟會孕育出何種結果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.48,0:00:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在誰也不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 12
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}來自京都的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由於總督的圍剿作戰 日本解放戰線基本上已經滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逃亡中的餘黨也陸續被抓獲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:23.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這算是諷刺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.23,0:02:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我軍此時正為如何重振而苦惱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我並沒有這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.57,0:02:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 當初佔領後實施的政策本身就有問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.84,0:02:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,AREA-11的地下鐵路網、礦山、礦道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.91,0:02:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼無人監管?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,貧民區的戶籍管理和各市的管轄範圍還是那麼含混不清
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反政府勢力的溫床就這麼被放任不管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個… 由於地下鐵路幾乎遍佈全國
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.51,0:02:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若要插手管理到租界以外的地方的話  預算就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使明知會成為恐怖分子的據點和逃跑路線也依然如此嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這是克洛維斯殿下的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:03:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 殿下指示 若過於強硬鎮壓 會導致內亂頻發
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會給中華聯邦可趁之機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是已經給了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的勢力正在不斷增強
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事務次官
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在內政省的行政架構內
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有著負責這個AREA自治的ELEVEN代表
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個被稱為NAC的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在前幾天的圍剿中 雖然想抓住NAC的把柄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但可惜資料都已被埋在沙土之下了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.31,0:03:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然而其嫌疑重大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若是先把他們鎮壓了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 名門和財閥的集合體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:34.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經是歷史的遺物了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.39,0:03:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請…請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這終究只不過是謠傳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.34,0:03:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒有真憑實據
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把他們鎮壓了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ELEVEN的經濟就會止步不前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.21,0:03:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對本國的稅收也會造成影響
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且讓NUMBERS管理NUMBERS是帝國的大原則
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼黑之騎士團的搜索呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從殘留下的挖掘機械(Shield Machine)來看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:04:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以判明成田的事是ZERO所為
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:03.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但除了團員屍骸以外 找不到更多的線索
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能對京都出手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又無法把ZERO逼入絕境
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從結果上來看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是所謂的無能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到布里塔尼亞的皇女竟如此厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,解放戰線分裂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本的希望之火已經熄滅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還未可斷言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說還在逃亡中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但籐堂還健在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:27.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說連無賴·改也失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒有希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有希望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑之騎士團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅蓮二式也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自從樞木朱雀救出事件以來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您對ZERO很執著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由於特拉法爾加(Trafalgar)戰役的敗北
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.66,0:04:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[1805年,在納爾遜指揮下的英國艦隊於直布羅陀海峽西北的\N特拉法爾加角擊敗法國和西班牙聯合艦隊的海戰。挫敗了拿破侖\N登陸英國本土的作戰計劃。英國掌握了制海權，納爾遜戰死。]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊麗莎白三世被革命勢力圍困在愛丁堡…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}當時布里塔尼亞軍鎮守在殖民地美洲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}也就是我們現在的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 心事重重的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:13.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,便秘? 宿醉?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:17.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼是因為魯魯修不在而感到寂寞?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,應該說是… 卡蓮也和他一起缺席了 又一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真悠閒啊 全世界都在討論前天的成田事件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀今天仍然因此請假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但對我來說 魯魯和卡蓮的事更成問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真可愛啊 莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是喜歡你這種性格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請別拿我尋開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說嘛 你直說不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,『我喜歡你』
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.15,0:05:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這可不行啊! 不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.78,0:05:55.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被拒絕了該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定連普通朋友也做不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也用不著… 笑得那麼誇張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是很開心呢 現在這個地方 現在的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還是稍微有點覺悟的好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.23,0:06:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不變的事物在哪兒都是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 不要變得那麼嚴肅嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果無論如何都想知道的話 乾脆去問本人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:27.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你是怎麼想的?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯…魯魯?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天不是休息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉稍微有點發燒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咲世子白天有點事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小娜娜的情況好點了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會長 那個文件…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,分發到各年級的各個班上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是這麼會使喚人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有個能幹的部下真是幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,部下?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 也還真是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 會長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣對心臟不好啊 那種…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧? 門票…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那些文件裡有沒有混雜我的信?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.39,0:07:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少胡思亂想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說 那傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我做到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他會來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒有拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:07:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一起去聽音樂會而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,僅此而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這是個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝了 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,京都稱讚我們很好地使用了紅蓮二式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是感動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 卻被那個白色機甲…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要介意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,平手啦 平手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莉她怎麼了 突然間…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸單身赴任去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不想讓我寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以經常會給我送來這些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說… 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,情書
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈? 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都說這傢伙不懂什麼叫開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玉城你笑得太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,京都來的詔書
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說非常希望與我們直接會面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是需要如此大驚小怪的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如此大驚小怪? 那可是京都啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果得到他們承認的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:08:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,將會獲得資金援助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:01.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們拮据的財政也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,財政?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果按我計劃的預算來辦的話 應該沒問題才對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我的錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已經是大組織了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人員增加的事可是預料之外的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,裝成大人物帶著新人縱情奢侈也是預料之外?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是知道的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們去了哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.78,0:09:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦? 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總而言之 今後會計的工作就改由扇負責
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.68,0:09:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以來錢都是交給我來管的 現在卻要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若想讓人信任的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就拿出相應的成果來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什麼資格說我?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.65,0:09:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自稱是同伴 卻連臉都不給我們看的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣啊 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,慢著 你這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:45.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的真面目是什麼無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO有著比那個柯內莉婭更勝一籌的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.54,0:09:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我們黑之騎士團的首領啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還需要其他什麼來證明嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是妮娜…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果身體不舒服的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:16.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛 我們本來是直人的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:25.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果身為妹妹的卡蓮都不介意的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為作為首領二代的你把位子讓給他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在成田的時候大家也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那時幾乎是脅迫了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然對我們這些幹部也保密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.76,0:10:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已將可能的範圍縮小到12人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之後就是抽中哪根簽的問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是需要隨機應變嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才說了些冒失的話 實在是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡蓮 你也想知道我的真面目嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人 可是知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.89,0:11:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,燒好像已經退了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,或許只是身體任性了一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,任性?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近心裡一直有種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥好像要去很遠的地方似的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以可能是身體希望得到照顧 自然地配合了一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無論發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我永遠都會在你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.79,0:11:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我再任性一下可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請再握著我的手一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若是這樣獨自睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得又會做那個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:13.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有事想要拜託我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.62,0:12:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我會按照你給我的提示行動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無論京都那邊的意圖是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:23.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我都想要得到那些人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這是你的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且對你的生存來說是必要的話 我也可以幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C. 我需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.34,0:12:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 這是你忘了的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是今天什麼時候能回來都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,準備打電話拒絕她而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,契約就應該要遵守啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 正好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 魯魯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:13:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,關於今天的約會 我可能會遲到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 肯定沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 肯定會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[東京租界中央單軌鐵路線  至成田]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要把其他的幹部也帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,主人是這麼吩咐的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了以防萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:21.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我讓他們在周圍警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.41,0:13:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上就去叫他們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 在此之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,破損較嚴重的屍體送到第二帳篷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有遺物的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請盡快確認其身份
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已確認身份的送到第一帳篷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,並以登記發現的場所與時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:39.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第二醫療班馬上就要到達
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現場作業人員立刻趕往臨設帳篷…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的在嗎  她… 在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.37,0:13:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忘掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.56,0:13:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,官方資料裡她已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經滿足了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,屍體發掘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的話 希望能讓我繼續救援作業
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼在你死心之前 請自便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這怎麼說也算是柯內莉婭殿下的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,羅伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO…黑之騎士團到底想要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:16.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他們以這種犧牲為代價
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底想要成就何種偉業?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是正義的使者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按照他本人的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.06,0:14:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這算是正義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會想要討論『什麼是正義』這種讓人害臊的理論吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們好歹也算是軍人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Energy Filler的更換
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,塞希爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我調查過了 純血派的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:53.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.23,0:14:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對  是輻射波動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.18,0:14:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到居然協助敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個拉庫夏塔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人的機師也是S級的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在朱雀精神仍不穩定的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再次和這種對手戰鬥的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想說贏不了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.78,0:15:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經過了很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還要開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微冷靜一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不像話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:25.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在上升
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給各位帶來諸多不便了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.52,0:15:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,主人已恭候多時
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡… 是富士礦山
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能來得到這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是不會有錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這座山 這個形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是說 這個下面就有Sakuradite?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:16:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誘發戰爭的罪魁禍首
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡 若發現入侵者 可是格殺勿論的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到居然把勢力滲透到這種地方來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:08.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,京都果然厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很醜惡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,過去曾經如此山清水秀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以流水清澈 綠秀富饒而著稱的靈峰富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在也向帝國低頭屈服 任憑其不斷凌辱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全就是雖仍生存卻被不斷凌辱的我們日本的寫照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:26.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是何等可悲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:30.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不以真面目面對你們 我為此無禮而道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是ZERO 這點你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須得看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我看看吧 你的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO賜予了我們力量與勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叫扇的是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:16:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:16:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.26,0:17:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你把ZERO的假面拿下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,扇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我也想相信… 你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 請讓我相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,女…女人!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:22.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人不是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我見過她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾見過她和ZERO在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你  不是日本人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,YES 京都的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.94,0:17:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,桐原泰三
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.67,0:17:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不能讓知道大人真面目的人活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,更不用說她還不是日本人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這和我無關啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是軟弱啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:17:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且行事手段和思想都太過迂腐了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.36,0:18:03.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  你們才贏不了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:07.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:09.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會被遙控射擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:11.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了 誰也不許動手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,桐原泰三
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Sakuradite採掘業務參與者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,桐原產業的創始人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.69,0:18:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,樞木政權的幕後中心人物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 戰敗後搖身一變
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:28.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成為支持殖民地統治的積極協力者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.20,0:18:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人稱 『賣國賊桐原』
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 其真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卻是管理全國抵抗組織的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,京都六家的要人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,陽奉陰違
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真穩妥的手段呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.40,0:18:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙 不得對大人無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.13,0:18:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誠如您所猜測
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我  不是日本人!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:52.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得不能讓我們看到臉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:18:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然並非生為日本人 為何要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底有什麼企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:02.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亞的毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:06.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能實現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.86,0:19:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就憑你可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要說為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有著必須那樣做的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對象是你實在是太幸運了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.52,0:19:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,桐原公
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是八年前被送來作為人質的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.99,0:19:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當時承蒙您多方照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果交涉對象是其他人的話 你會把他當作人質吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做的 僅僅是提出願望而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:44.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,八年前的種子開花了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.53,0:19:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,扇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,此人毫無疑問是布里塔尼亞的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其不願顯露面容的理由我也瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以保證
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟隨ZERO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,據點隱蔽以及情報搜尋這些我們也會協助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,萬分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝 桐原公
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.76,0:20:16.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要踏上 修羅之路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果 這是我的命運的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第2  第5  第7  第8  第9小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續在管理總部進行確認作業
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.11,0:20:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,菲尼特的拼法是這樣的話 確實是這位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遺體在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 由於現在情況特殊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不… 不會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.99,0:20:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼請您確認
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然已經不在了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之一切從現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:21:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑之騎士團真正成為如我所願而行動的組織了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 對不起我遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為你已經走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 先不管那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.29,0:21:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總而言之先找個避雨的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.87,0:21:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO是弱者的同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.06,0:21:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是… 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:35.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 為什麼要殺了我爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.78,0:21:39.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸他 很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.47,0:21:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從來都沒有打過我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.26,0:21:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼壞事都沒有做過…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 卻被活埋了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,痛苦地窒息而死…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:51.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.17,0:21:53.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼爸爸要拋下我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.89,0:21:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:21:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.97,0:21:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.79,0:22:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你 魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.42,0:22:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.33,0:23:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.77,0:23:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行動的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.55,0:23:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.54,0:23:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卻又為何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.22,0:23:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從舞台上消失是很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.20,0:24:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要捨棄ZERO這一存在就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.30,0:24:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要封住桐原的口
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.91,0:24:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能變回魯魯修·蘭佩魯基
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.92,0:24:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是… 可是…
